{"data": [{"id": "4745506", "title": "How Would A Government Shutdown Affect Market Volatility?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electronic highway billboard with government shutdown ahead warning\" data-id=\"1669041839\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Stephen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Brian Levitt, Global Market Strategist</em></p> <p>With much of the country looking ahead to the holidays, the US government could be on the verge of a shutdown. Congress, urged by incoming president Donald Trump, opposed a three-month extension to the current budget. Without</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745506-how-government-shutdown-affect-market-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745496", "title": "Western Union: Deep Value And Dividend Income", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Western Union Office in Prague.\" data-id=\"1943169915\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">VIDOK</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The Western Union Company provides money movement and payment services worldwide, focused mostly on consumer cross border money transfers and consumer financial services including bill payment, money orders, and digital wallets. The company started out in communication services but has transformed over</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745496-western-union-deep-value-and-dividend-income", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:15:15", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745502", "title": "Could A New Misery Index Help Explain The Election Outcome?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oversized vote and ballot box surrounded by people\" data-id=\"2158306529\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In 1970, everyone was feeling bad about the economy. How bad? To put a number to the pervasively negative vibe, Arthur Okun created the \"misery index:\" the sum of inflation and unemployment rates.</p> <p>But now everyone is puzzled. Why</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745502-new-misery-index-help-explain-election-outcome", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745493", "title": "Micron Q1 Review: Strong AI Demand Means I'm Still Bullish (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Taiwan Micron Technology Company plant.\" data-id=\"1660789089\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BING-JHEN HONG/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Micron Technology (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>) fell 16% following earnings, with their Q2 2025 revenue guidance of $7.7 billion to $8.1 billion missing estimates and driving the selloff. This was well <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387691-micron-tumbles-weak-q2-forecast-fails-to-overcome-q1-results\">below</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745493-micron-stock-q1-review-strong-ai-demand-still-bullish-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 09:59:21", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745492", "title": "Struggling For Air: Quipt Home Medical's Growth Hurdles And Recovery Potential", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Portrait of senior man enjoying an autumn day in the forest.\" data-id=\"1291085789\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"7360px\" height=\"4843px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DjelicS</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p><strong>Quipt Home Medical (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QIPT\" title=\"Quipt Home Medical Corp.\">QIPT</a></span>)</strong> is one of those under-the-radar companies that answers a need in people\u2019s daily life by delivering in-home respiratory care and durable medical equipment to 135 centers in 26 states. They\u2019re all about respirators, and with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745492-struggling-for-air-quipt-home-medical-stock-growth-hurdles-recovery-potential-hold-for-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 09:47:02", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745498", "title": "CB Leading Economic Index: Small Rise In November", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man in a business meeting using an interactive screen while giving a presentation\" data-id=\"1468025006\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The latest <a href=\"https://www.conference-board.org/topics/us-leading-indicators\" rel=\"noopener noopener\">Conference Board Leading Economic Index</a> (LEI) increased slightly in November. The index rose 0.3% from the previous month to 99.7 after eight consecutive monthly declines.</p> <blockquote><p>\"The US LEI rose in November for the first time since February</p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745498-cb-leading-economic-index-small-rise-november", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 09:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745491", "title": "Okeanis Eco Tankers: Targeting Efficiency Gains With One Of The Youngest Fleets In The Industry", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view on the industrial cargo ship unloading at the petroleum terminal in New Jersey, on the Arthur Kill tidal strait at the border with New York State.\" data-id=\"1324124760\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"863px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Alex Potemkin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Description</h2> <p>Okeanis Eco Tankers (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ECO\" title=\"Okeanis Eco Tankers Corp.\">ECO</a></span>) owns a fleet of 14 crude oil tankers with a total capacity of 3.5 million DWT. Compared to other players in the industry, Okeanis is relatively small. For example, once the six vessels under orders are</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745491-okeanis-eco-tankers-targeting-efficiency-gains-one-of-youngest-fleet-in-industry", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 09:07:51", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745490", "title": "Chipotle: In A Tough Spot As Price Hikes May Trigger Further Sales Deterioration", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_2159351616.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Massachusetts, USA - 14 June 2024. General view of the Chipotle mexican grill logo sign on an cafe building exterior\" data-id=\"2159351616\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_2159351616.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_2159351616.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_2159351616.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_2159351616.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_2159351616.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_2159351616.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159351616/image_215935161